The Board and the Director solicit and evaluate nominations for submission to the President. Nominations accompanied
by biographical informational may be forwarded to the Chairman, National Science Board, 4201 Wilson Boulevard,
Arlington, VA, 22230, no later than January 6, 1995.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Any questions should be directed to Mrs. Susan E. Fannoney, Staff Assistant, National Science Board (703/306&hyph;2000).

